# Files that execute on Linux (shebangs, cloud-init, systemd) must keep LF
# even on Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true would otherwise produce
# CRLF working files, and `npm pack` ships the working tree verbatim —
# a CRLF shebang breaks /usr/bin/env on the deployed VM).
bin/cli.js   text eol=lf
*.sh         text eol=lf
*.tftpl      text eol=lf
*.service    text eol=lf
